description: When working with Gradle modules
globs: ["**/build.gradle","**/build.gradle.kts","**/settings.gradle","**/settings.gradle.kts"]
alwaysApply: false
---
All gradle modules should follow one of the following patterns, where MODULE_NAME is replaced with the specific name for that module: feature/MODULE_NAME/public, feature/MODULE_NAME/internal, feature/MODULE_NAME/test, library/MODULE_NAME/public, library/MODULE_NAME/internal, or library/MODULE_NAME/test